column5: Id like to think I did my part by posting and reposting pics, then adding numerous food threads???  OFC is a really great forum?

We will be arriving at 85,000,000 views sometime before noon today.  That's almost unheard of in fishing site circles. We'd like to thank everyone who has participated in this community's success. It's just great to be a part of this community. Thank you all!
